        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1976872708" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer10555105365084317247"><b>3.5 Stars! </b><br/><br/>Sometimes our lives are dependent upon Making Choices! And that too, Right ones!<br/><br/>Question is <b>What is right and what is not? </b><br/><br/><img src='https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/hostedimages/1492681394i/22540953.jpg' class='gr-hostedUserImg'/><br/><br/>An honest and heart-shaking book.<br/><br/>Ravi, a pragmatic, responsible and reasonable man, who lives a structured lifestyle, has two children and divorced. He is now looking for someone whom he can call his soulmate. <br/><br/>He can overcome everything but the burns of his past have left marks that cannot be removed easily. His past is not only accountable for the turmoils in his</span>
  <span id="freeText10555105365084317247" style="display:none"><b>3.5 Stars! </b><br><br>Sometimes our lives are dependent upon Making Choices! And that too, Right ones!<br><br>Question is <b>What is right and what is not? </b><br><br><img src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/hostedimages/1492681394i/22540953.jpg" class="gr-hostedUserImg"><br><br>An honest and heart-shaking book.<br><br>Ravi, a pragmatic, responsible and reasonable man, who lives a structured lifestyle, has two children and divorced. He is now looking for someone whom he can call his soulmate. <br><br>He can overcome everything but the burns of his past have left marks that cannot be removed easily. His past is not only accountable for the turmoils in his present life but also it is tormenting him beyond the bearable line. Anyone who will enter into his life would be a savior. <br><br>Olivia becomes just that. And he couldn't prevent himself falling head over heels for her. <br><br>Olivia too, has a bleeding past of her own. Her children have suffered too. Both of them are determined to have met their soulmates. What decisions Ravi will make would influence both sets of children as well as themselves.<br><br>The impact that this book has on you, is thoughtful and profound. If you are reading this book while looking for a life partner, it would definitely prosper your thought procedure. <br><br>Much research has been done by the author before he penned down his thoughts. <br><br>Flow of the story, realistic characters and intuitive writing style - all of them were enough to make me engaged to Chase of Choices to the very end. <br><br>Wrapped up with surprises and intellectual writing, Chase of Choises provides you a beneficial and sagacious read. Some moments push you to weep your heart out and others give you the sensible emotional support. <br><br>The difficulties we confront when taking important decisions and how they affect our lives, all these prospects has been fabricated in a beautiful manner. Coming to the philosophical side of this novel, anyone would be impressed by the technique with which the narrator has told the tale. <br><br>Recommended to those who want to see a man gripped in turbulence of emotions.</span>
