<div id="review_1262883480" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/1262883480" />
    <a title="Hari Parameshwar" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/36785785-hari-parameshwar"><img alt="Hari Parameshwar" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1446655341p2/36785785.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/1262883480?book_show_action=true">Apr 23, 2015</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Hari Parameshwar" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Hari Parameshwar" href="/user/show/36785785-hari-parameshwar">Hari Parameshwar</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span> (Review from the author)


        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1262883480" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer3589902241111079072"><br/>The New Indian Express: <br/><br/>&quot;Chase of Choices is an emotional whirlwind on the complexities of life. Dotted with wisdom and musings from life, Chase of Choices tells us how, sometimes, the decisions taken by us can turn our life upside down....<br/><br/>....We suggest you pick up the book on a lovely rainy day, keep an unlimited supply of chai and keep reading this unputdownable book.&quot;<br/><br/><br/>Read the complete review here: <a target='_blank' rel='noopener nofollow' href='http://www.newindianexpress.com/lifestyle/books/2014/11/22/The-Long-Pursuit-of-Elusive-Love/article2534631.ece'>http://www.newindianexpress.com/lifes...</a><br/></span>
  <span id="freeText3589902241111079072" style="display:none"><br />The New Indian Express: <br /><br />"Chase of Choices is an emotional whirlwind on the complexities of life. Dotted with wisdom and musings from life, Chase of Choices tells us how, sometimes, the decisions taken by us can turn our life upside down....<br /><br />....We suggest you pick up the book on a lovely rainy day, keep an unlimited supply of chai and keep reading this unputdownable book."<br /><br /><br />Read the complete review here: <a target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow" href="http://www.newindianexpress.com/lifestyle/books/2014/11/22/The-Long-Pursuit-of-Elusive-Love/article2534631.ece">http://www.newindianexpress.com/lifes...</a><br /></span>
