  <span id="freeText4744422117955732991" style="display:none">Thank you Hari parameshwar for giving me this copy as authors choice and so many more the autograph.<br /><br />Ravi Raj Nambiar is divorced, single parent, is in search of wife through martimotal portal, who can play mother role of his two children, especially for his daughter. in the journey of finding suitable wife, which is never ending quest, he met many choices, I mean candiates.<br /><br />Meenu, cute face, short hair, who is in his mind, who is interested in marrying ravi and somewhat is little strange. (I thing she have split personality). and then there is Anjali (I was secretly rooting for her with ravi), charming, with appealing eyes and a wide smile, sensible, poetess, with child like voice, and Priya menon.<br /><br /><br />But everything left aside when he got voice message from American women called Olivia Claire O'Neil, white women, with 2 children of her own, who wants to marry Indian man and settled down in India. she feels ravi is her soulmate for whom she longed for. with so many choice, who he will and should settle down with.<br /><br />---------------------<br />For more check out my blog <br />asmaaam.wordpress.com<br /></span>
