<div id="review_2988534582" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/2988534582" />
    <a title="Sabreena Shah" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/103185084-sabreena-shah"><img alt="Sabreena Shah" src="https://s.gr-assets.com/assets/nophoto/user/u_50x66-632230dc9882b4352d753eedf9396530.png" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/2988534582?book_show_action=true">Sep 23, 2019</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Sabreena Shah" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Sabreena Shah" href="/user/show/103185084-sabreena-shah">Sabreena Shah</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2988534582" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer7182868867625678009">This book is so true to its title and raw! I not only loved this one but could relate to Olivia and her spontaneity. More than love, this book tells us how we stumble across choices in our life and choosing the right choice makes or breaks our future. In love with this author! </span>

          </span>
        </div>


      <div class="reviewFooter uitext buttons">
          

